112
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:37,206
Congratulations on getting married!

113
00:07:37,874 --> 00:07:40,460
<i>Shortly after, they had a son.</i>

114
00:07:42,628 --> 00:07:45,506
<i>The successful husband and the wise wife.</i>

115
00:07:46,174 --> 00:07:51,137
<i>And with an adorable child, he had</i>
<i>all he needed to make a happy family.</i>

116
00:07:55,433 --> 00:07:56,601
<i>Until one day…</i>

117
00:07:58,936 --> 00:08:00,605
<i>Jeon Sang-ho went missing.</i>

118
00:08:11,616 --> 00:08:15,870
<i>His parents found it odd that they were</i>
<i>unable to reach him and called the police.</i>

119
00:08:15,953 --> 00:08:16,954
Come and check this.

120
00:08:18,623 --> 00:08:20,291
- This is blood, isn't it?
- Yes.

121
00:08:21,459 --> 00:08:23,753
<i>Bloodstains found in the grout lines</i>
<i>on the living room floor</i>

122
00:08:24,337 --> 00:08:26,297
<i>turned out to be Jeon Sang-ho's,</i>

123
00:08:26,881 --> 00:08:29,926
<i>and the missing person case</i>
<i>turned into a murder case.</i>

124
00:08:32,762 --> 00:08:34,972
I was out running that evening.

125
00:08:35,056 --> 00:08:36,307
Right over there…

126
00:08:46,192 --> 00:08:50,112
Based on her psychiatric records,

127
00:08:50,196 --> 00:08:53,991
